      <p>This was a massive point of contention between product owners. Workhub has had lots of different UI over the years trying to solve this problem (collapsible sections, indefinite indenting, + many more). We opted for a simple three-level light indent matched up to sticky headers with hot keys that jump between.</p>
      <p>This had immediate positive feedback in demos and continues to perform well with users in the wild.</p>
